in writing. - (FR) Following the large-scale safety recall of Chinese-made toys by the US manufacturer Mattel the European Commission is now taking stock of its product safety legislation, especially where imported toys are concerned.
The European system of regulation in this area is solid enough, with RAPEX and the CE mark, but it needs to be strengthened.
