It is glaringly obvious that the European Union must lay down precise rules and actively regulate who will be admitted to work in the EU.
We all know that Europe is already experiencing a 'demographic winter' and urgently requires manpower from non-member countries.
However, it is absolutely vital that we admit only skilled labour and I propose that we select professions which are in short supply on the labour market in Europe.
